{"tid":1677113,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"諗過考警隊受阻阿叻：秀姑嗌離婚！","createTime":"2019-10-27T01:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:42:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9e89b7de9e3bffb1031d6b909c2b101c76804b","tid":1677113,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"藝人陳百祥（阿叻）昨晚到電視城出席《善心滿載仁愛堂》記者會，講到日前往警署打氣的短片在網上瘋傳，片中他指若自己做警務處長，一早已開槍，引來廣泛討論，他對此說：「呢個世界一向有唔同意見，我唔係教人點樣做，亦唔使人教我點做，呢啲就係民主自由。（你真係有興趣做警務處長？）68年時考過警隊，但我一話做，秀姑就話離婚，朋友笑我會『升官發財冇老婆』。（你贊成警方早啲開槍？）開唔開槍係制度問題，見到暴徒掟彈令人成身燒着晒，咁樣唔開槍呀？既然暴力升級，警方都要升級。」又認為馬蹄露及任何人遇襲都無辜。<br />\n<br />\n早前譚詠麟（阿倫）撐警同樣引起議論，問到會否擔心有同一遭遇？阿叻說：「我膽生毛，驚咩呀？我上冇高堂，下冇子女。（有冇餐廳拒絕你入去？）有人話如果我入去，放低錢幫我埋單呀！」<br />\n<br />\n陳庭欣結婚沖喜？<br />\n同場的陳庭欣日前開車時被的士撞車尾，她表示沒大礙，但直言近半年運氣差，可能要找玄學家指點迷津，問到若對方提議結婚？她說：「睇吓係咪幫到，但唔係我話結就結！（男友心痛？）唔知呢，咁佢都好擔心。」至於丁子朗在新劇《解決師》大騷肌肉，他表示是監製要求：「本身有肌肉喺度，但拍嗰陣操行啲！（你嘅肌肉定係馮盈盈露背吸引？）冇得比，就算佢除衫，大家都留意佢個樣先，因為太靚！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KCAFodGi0TYb4fPrcWQqIQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/6898ac89e703136a10a772dcf7cf889d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKCAFodGi0TYb4fPrcWQqIQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F6898ac89e703136a10a772dcf7cf889d&h=73a61fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AB%97%E9%81%8E%E8%80%83%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB%E9%98%BF%E5%8F%BB-%E7%A7%80%E5%A7%91%E5%97%8C%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A-214500962.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AB%2597%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2598%25BB%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%258F%25BB-%25E7%25A7%2580%25E5%25A7%2591%25E5%2597%258C%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A9%259A-214500962.html&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e39b3468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AB%97%E9%81%8E%E8%80%83%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB%E9%98%BF%E5%8F%BB-%E7%A7%80%E5%A7%91%E5%97%8C%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A-214500962.html</a>"},{"pid":"34d4083ada4f3dd18eea921567896f93d261441a","tid":1677113,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyfzGuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyfzGuv.jpg&h=efeca98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去考大陸公安啦屌"},{"pid":"ff801ded20b9dc46529de44b276c0989dd30f6f1","tid":1677113,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"Remember remember, the 5th of November. 11月5日 18區 V煞營火晚會！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677120</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a90c36709648093c962a416480119f0b5ea99e2b","tid":1677113,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"68年你結左緍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6338fabec85044e86e99fbbdddc863754da257","tid":1677113,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a90c36709648093c962a416480119f0b5ea99e2b","tid":1677113,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"68年你結左緍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"條友真係up得就up"}]}